  "description": "<p>\n\t<strong>1. It&rsquo;ll look good on your CV</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/07/24/1de49f37ac89789cced75e5d10a83500.jpg\" /></strong></p>\n<p>\n\tIf you can explore a new country at the same time as picking up the international skills to gain a decent graduate job, then that&rsquo;s pretty good going.<strong>给你的简历增添光彩<br />\n\t</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t你即可以探索一个新的国度，同时也可以获得新的国际化技能，毕业后能找到更加体面的工作。留学真的是一个不错的选择。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>2. Brush up on your language skills</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tRemember the foreign language skills you picked up in school? No, me neither. Refresh them by studying abroad; you might be surprised at how much you remember.<strong></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>加强你的语言技能<br />\n\t</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t你是不是已经忘记自己在学校学过的语言技能了？我也忘了。留学可以让你把这些技能重新捡起来，你会被自己惊艳到哦！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>3. Meet a diverse range of people</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/07/24/7bc05e49c8a802c578ae098ce474f4af.jpg\" /></strong></p>\n<p>\n\tYour exposure to many different types of people will not only help you to develop your people skills, but it will also give you a firmer knowledge of others, both friend and foe.<strong></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>遇到不同的人<br />\n\t</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t你会遇到不同类型的人，既能提升你的人际交往能力，也能让你更好地了解别人，不管是朋友还是敌人。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>4. Study and learn differently</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tOften those studying abroad will experience a completely new way of teaching. This can be daunting, but it will also open your mind to new ways of learning.<strong></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>新的学习方式<br />\n\t</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t出国留学，你将会体验不同的教学方式。你可能会困惑，但是新的教学方式会开启你的心智，让你掌握新的学习方法。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>5. Gain independence</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/07/24/c5b918928fa40fa565c2a4739df97c5d.jpg\" /></strong></p>\n<p>\n\tIt&rsquo;s not easy being independent, but it&rsquo;s also a heck of a lot better than living with your parents as a 20-something.<strong>变得独立<br />\n\t</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t独立并不简单&mdash;&mdash;但是作为一个20多岁的成年人，独立总好过与父母同住。</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">看到这些，你是不是心动了呢？</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你是否也向往着美国的自由女神像，英伦的大本钟，澳洲的考拉和袋鼠？</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你是否也憧憬着与世界各地的同学和教授们侃侃而谈，指点江山，激扬文字？</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你是否也渴望着离开父母的庇佑，酣畅淋漓地靠自己去生活，去奋斗，甚至&hellip;&hellip;去跌倒，去犯错？</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px;\">你是否也在犹疑和不知所措，不知该如何踏出这</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">关键的第一步</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px;\">？</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">那你还在等什么，赶紧打开&ldquo;<span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">沪江留学助手</span>&rdquo;为自己规划一条光明的留学路吧！</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #a9a9a9;\">&darr;一分钟完成简短测评&darr;</span></strong></span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img height=\"449\" src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/07/24/ed6df601641ab30af82a4b1c8ab72910.jpg\" width=\"448\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: #a9a9a9;\"><br />\n\t</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #a9a9a9;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #a9a9a9;\">&darr;</span></strong></span></strong>获取各项留学指标评分<strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #a9a9a9;\">&darr;</span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: #a9a9a9;\"><img height=\"882\" src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/07/24/2fddb